objects.name: Instructions
objects.string:
Arrow keys to move
Space to jump

Hold left or right against a
green wall to slowly slide
down it, press jump to
wall jump

Press shift when in the air
and holding left or right
to dash in a direction

Press G to activate god mode.

objects.name: wallslide
objects.string:
To slide down a wall:
Jump towards it and hold direction.
Press jump whilst sliding to perform a wall jump.

objects.name: gtext
objects.string: Press G to activate godmode. (Invulnerability and infinite jumps)

objects.name: tiptext
objects.string: Test out controls here before playing!

objects.name: credit
objects.string:
Assets by Kenney and Xelu
Music by Alex McCulloch

objects.name: Explanation
objects.string:
A challenging platformer, reach the flag in each stage.
Use precisely timed jumps and dashes to progress.

objects.name: hint
objects.string:
Tip: Hold space or shift to instantly jump or dash when next avaiable
Helpful to dash as soon as gaining a dash up or jump instantly off a wall.
